metadata.description: Data Type: Subsistence/Traditional Knowledge;   Subsistence survey data described by community codes and USGS 1:250,000 quad codes. This coverage has both a Polygon Attribute Table (PAT) and an Arc Attribute Table (AAT) with accompanying attributes.
